Author: SuperFruit
Title: [ANN] [ICO] SuperFruit - Blockchain for SuperFruit plantation & B2B platform
Body: Thank You for asking. Our main target is to increase the area of our superfruit plantations and production, followed by the goal of creating a Business to Business platform. (You can think of it as an "aliexpress" aimed on superfruits and other superfoods)  Why are We doing this? We want to make superfoods more accessible to people. Is there an easy way to get superfoods in Your city/town?  You can find more about our project in our Whitepaper and if it is not enough, send us an email with specific questions or keep this feed going.

Author: megenageda
Title: [ANN] [ICO] SuperFruit - Blockchain for SuperFruit plantation & B2B platform
Body: What are the special things about your project? What makes it better than others?

Author: SuperFruit
Title: [ANN] [ICO] SuperFruit - Blockchain for SuperFruit plantation & B2B platform
Body: Great question. Our main pillar are our products themselves, because they are organic and contain many essential substances our bodies need. Don't You think more people should be able to get quality food directly from local farmers? Our goal is simple - make an nature-friendly environment for organic farmers to sell their products aswell as expanding our own plantations in order to produce more superfruit.  The other one is a tough one, it is not our duty to judge ourselves by others, but maybe you can be more specific? Cryptomarket is a vast place and there are many competitors, such as we are. Do You know about similar projects? If so, please share it with us, so we can learn and make our products even better for all.

Author: thedarkk
Title: [ANN] [ICO] SuperFruit - Blockchain for SuperFruit plantation & B2B platform
Body: I like the idea of your project. Still, there are some questions. In what countries the project will be implemented and how will you conduct the delivery? And one more: do you offer fresh fruits or packaged ones (dried ones or sth else)?

Author: SuperFruit
Title: [ANN] [ICO] SuperFruit - Blockchain for SuperFruit plantation & B2B platform
Body: We are happy to hear that! The project will begin its implentation in South America, since it is our region and will further expand to Europe, Asia and rest of the world, if everything goes as planned. We already have shipping (and air-shipping) contracts with third parties, that are ready to begin once we have a significant amount of superfruit at our disposal. So far we are ready to ship only packaged (dried) products, but if the ICO turns out succesful, we will be able to ship fresh fruit to almost any part of the world.  Great questions, if You would like to know more, don't hesitate to keep this feed alive.
